description:
What if Rapunzel's mother had drank a potion from the wrong flower? With her mysterious hairs comes dangerous magical powers. A reimagined darker story of Disney's Tangled told through silhouette and animation.

Inspired by The New York Times Best-Selling Series, A Twisted Tales, available wherever books are sold.
